The paper describes a method for image classification using a deep neural network, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) sub-categories. The focus of the paper is on breast cancer grading, which is a medical imaging application that could also fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
